{"tid":1518153,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"1945年8月30日，夏愨率領皇家海軍特遣艦隊抵達香港，香港重光","createTime":"2019-08-30T07:04:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T09:22:16.000Z","uid":32244,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1b59159a4b2fc4d0f7d4b13eb6aa49f515f5dffb","tid":1518153,"uid":32244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:04:08.000Z","msg":"1945年8月30日，夏慤率領以「HMS不屈號」為首的分遣艦隊駛入維多利亞港，在香港升起了英國國旗，象徵日本正式結束在香港的管治；從那日開始，至1997年香港主權移交以前，港府將每年的8月30日定為重光紀念日，以作紀念。在同日晚上，夏慤又隨詹遜等人到赤柱參加感恩崇拜。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%A4%8F%E6%85%A4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%25A4%258F%25E6%2585%25A4&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUigexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=696e1a11\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%A4%8F%E6%85%A4</a>"},{"pid":"a54c3991ffe2a7f054a030a79d9fa359fc462082","tid":1518153,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:04:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k29z7U2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk29z7U2.gif&h=78a316aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUigexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=e5416400\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUigexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=8c4131ac\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=zmS1uFJnVw4lvQjuvPvUigexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=7b41dc69\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"afc1b9fa9a14500a81